🇬🇧 English

This project is a ticketing and IT request management system, built for the company Behin Roshd. Its main goal is to properly manage internal technical issues and prevent time and workforce loss on unnecessary tasks.

✨ Features
🔐 User registration and login
🎫 Employees can submit tickets (issues) to the IT department
👨‍💻 Dedicated IT staff panel to view and handle tickets
💬 Messaging system between the employee and the IT staff member for each ticket
📅 IT staff can schedule when a task will be completed (e.g. "will be done on such date, at such time")
📜 Full action history for each IT staff member, visible in the admin panel
🌐 Fully Persian, right-to-left (RTL) user interface
🛠️ Tech Stack
Backend: Django (Python)
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Database: SQLite
🚀 Getting Started
Clone the repository:
bash
git clone https://github.com/nbvali730-ai/helpdesk-ticketing.git
cd helpdesk-ticketing/helpdesk
Create and activate a virtual environment:
bash
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
Install the dependencies:
bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Run database migrations:
bash
python manage.py migrate
Start the development server:
bash
python manage.py runserver

The project will then be available at:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/
